Package: HRSWGS
Type: Package
Title: Hard Red Spring Wheat breeding Genomic Selection toolbox
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Charlotte", "Brault",
      email = "charlotte.brault@live.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Custom functions to help data wrangling and formatting
    for using genomic selection in hard red spring wheat breeding programs. 
    Format genotypic and phenotypic data, perform genomic prediction and communicate the results.
